2021 in the mail: 20 packets per household - and a weight gain
46.6 million packages arrived in Israel during 2021 - similar to 2020 •
The average weight per package is 435 grams - a 36% increase from 2020
The busiest month: December, when the average package weighed 524 grams.
In 2021, 46.6 million parcels of mail arrived in Israel, almost 20 parcels on average per household - this is according to the data of Israel Post obtained by Israel Today.
The number of packages arriving in 2021 is similar to 2020, when 46.5 million packages arrived in Israel, and lower than 2019 - when 61.6 million packages arrived.
However, this year there has been a jump of more than 36 percent a year in the weight of packages coming in from abroad.
In 2021, 20,253 tons of foreign products arrived in Israel, a jump of 36% compared to 14,860 tons in 2020 and 16,743 tons in 2019.
Changes in consumption habits
The average weight per pack has jumped by 60 percent in two years - from 272 grams in 2019 to 435 grams in 2021.
The surge in parcel weight is mainly driven by two main trends, both on the seller's side and the buyer's side: the major overseas shopping sites unify items for one delivery and no longer ship each product from the "shopping cart" in a separate package.
On the Israeli consumer's side, the quick delivery of the shipments, within a few days of ordering, supports the purchase of more everyday goods such as clothes and gifts, which the buyers wish to receive near the purchase.
In 2021, as in 2020 and 2019, the month with the highest number of packages arriving from abroad and the highest number of items is December, with 4.2 million packages weighing a total of 2,200 tons.
In December, the average weight per pack was 524 grams, 20 percent higher than the annual average.
The Black Friday effect.
More packages arrived in December than in any other month, likely in the wake of November's shopping holidays, such as Chinese Singles' Day, Black Friday and Cyber Monday.
Big orders start arriving in Israel within a week or two of purchase.
